            "description": "Variant of  https://shadertoy.com/view/3lt3DN . Better seen in fullscreen. try other textures in bufA.\nbottom: R,G= raw dFdx,y shows the 2x2 blocks\ntop: correction using the correct 3x3 cross neighborhood. Trick: store dFdx,y( f(u) ) and dFdx,y( f(u+1) )\n",
